#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta robots=\"noindex\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta robots=\"noindex\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<h1 id=\"verify-other\" class=\"step\">Verify that the other Tails is up-to-date</h1>\n"
msgstr "<h1 id=\"verify-other\" class=\"step\">Vérifier que l'autre Tails est à jour</h1>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To prevent\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">installing</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">upgrading to</span>\n"
"an outdated version of Tails with known security issues, make sure that the Tails you are\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">installing</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">upgrading</span>\n"
"from is up-to-date:\n"
msgstr ""
"Pour éviter\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">d'installer</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">de mettre à jour vers</span>\n"
"une version obsolète de Tails avec des problèmes de sécurité connus, assurez-vous que le Tails depuis lequel vous allez\n"
"<span class=\"pc-clone mac-clone\">installer</span>\n"
"<span class=\"upgrade-clone\">mettre à jour</span>\n"
"est à jour :\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Choose **Apps&nbsp;▸ Tails&nbsp;▸ About Tails**."
msgstr "Choisissez **Applications&nbsp;▸ Tails&nbsp;▸ À propos de Tails**."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Verify that you are running **Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/"
"stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]** released on [[!inline "
"pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_date\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]:"
msgstr ""
"Vérifiez que vous utilisez **Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/"
"stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]** qui est sorti le [[!"
"inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_date\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]] :"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"If you are running Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], continue with the next step."
msgstr ""
"Si vous utilisez Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], passez à l'étape suivante."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"If you are not running Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], click **Check for Upgrades**."
msgstr ""
"Si vous n'utilisez pas Tails [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" "
"raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]], cliquez sur *Check for Upgrades**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "     Apply all upgrades as requested.\n"
msgstr "     Appliquez toutes les mises à jour demandées.\n"

#, no-wrap
#~ msgid ""
#~ "   b. If you are not running [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]] then connect to the Internet\n"
#~ "   and to Tor. After a minute or two, *Tails Upgrader*\n"
#~ "   appears with instructions on how to upgrade. Apply all upgrades as requested.\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "   b. Si vous n'utilisez pas la version [[!inline pages=\"inc/stable_amd64_version\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]] connectez-vous à Internet\n"
#~ "   et à Tor. Après une minute ou deux, le *Tails Upgrader*\n"
#~ "   apparaît avec les instructions de mise à jour. Appliquez les mises à jour comme demandé.\n"

